Subject: Preliminary design ideas for covid 19 app mini project
Members: Shazor Shahid , Ryan Schneider

Deployment and Development:
Expo

Using Firebase in the later stages of the progress to add authentication module

------------
rough app architecture overview:

Expo (app development, deployment to Web, Android and iOS)
| -> backend built in Node.js
| -> connect to Firebase with Firebase JS SDK
    | -> Firebase - Database service
    | -> Firebase - Authentication (SSO - Google) service
| -> frontend built in HTML/CSS with JS elements
------------